room_title: Escape room "Cabin in the Woods" by Tampa Bay Escape Room in Tampa
room_description: While on a hiking trip with your friends, you stumble upon an old cabin in the woods. The thunder sends you running inside for shelter. You soon discover that this little cabin is not all that it appears. You decide you would rather brave the storm and attempt to leave, however, the door locks trapping you inside. Your mission: save your life and escape this little cabin within 60 minutes.
